        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 39. Labels. i Otostomus moritinctus Martens, 1893 ii Bulimus moussoni Pfeiffer, 1853 iii Bulimus muliebris Reeve, 1849 iv Bulimulus (Drymaeus) mossi E. A. Smith, 1896 v Bulimus munsterii d'Orbigny, 1837 vi Drymaeus multispira da Costa 1904 vii Bulimus musivus Pfeiffer, 1855." , "Figure 74. A Naesiotus eschariferus (Sowerby I, 1833), syntype NHMUK 1975153 (H = 18.4) B Naesiotus rugulosus (Sowerby I, 1838), lectotype NHMUK 1975176 (H = 20.5) C Naesiotus sculpturatus (Pfeiffer, 1846), lectotype NHMUK 1975174 (H = 14.1) D Naesiotus munsterii (d'Orbigny, 1837), syntype NHMUK 1854.12.4. (H = 21.7) E-G Drymaeus (Drymaeus) laxostylus (Rolle, 1904), holotype NHMUK 1922.2.23.32 (H = 39.9). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26806" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26750" .

